{"tid":768423,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"某啲歌一聽就會有翻以前第一次聽個首歌既季節感覺","createTime":"2018-08-05T11:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T18:02:02.000Z","uid":6640,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d601fc17b08a51e6703c2acb3c89450816dc423b","tid":768423,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"我一聽某隻歌就會去翻以前第一次聽呢首歌既季節<br />\n有無人都係咁？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/191851_3b8637d736c4bfe45ed96e48d0ba03bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F191851_3b8637d736c4bfe45ed96e48d0ba03bf.png&h=4e60fb24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如呢首 我第一次聽係秋天聽<br />\n每次聽都會有感覺係去翻秋冬天咁<br />\n好舒服 凍凍地 着長袖 <br />\n樹上面跌左好多黃左既樹葉係地下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9981dce73cc954a0393680bd1a1f5aae78b0b047","tid":768423,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"聽周杰倫d歌寧舍有畫面"},{"pid":"5c3bf86d39d24c31f5d642dc0821f24353448435","tid":768423,"uid":21204,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"楓"},{"pid":"4904a2f21bdc39a8eb0aa2bcb39f8f82866c332a","tid":768423,"uid":168551,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"以為得我一個會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾首歌某年夏天成日聽<br />\n而家一聽返就諗起嗰年夏天發生過嘅事<br />\n好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1eeec462ba976e71b92f6ff8f394387dc938f36","tid":768423,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9981dce73cc954a0393680bd1a1f5aae78b0b047","tid":768423,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"聽周杰倫d歌寧舍有畫面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"我唔太熟佢<br />\n不過佢都有一兩隻歌我都會有個季節感覺"},{"pid":"598e6348d8f