"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"我好多時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最深刻係赤城千葉 &mdash; 秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccdfa9a0ea7b96847fa5210032d763dc361d194","tid":768423,"uid":49456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"約定"},{"pid":"d0b7f63ff553212580146684cd7c251fbad4b316","tid":768423,"uid":6640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"仲有王苑之既小團圓<br />\n一聽就去左冬天 好委屈 好傷感"},{"pid":"5eadcfb76c7cc22f27ea92a7bb9e5f80d75af48f","tid":768423,"uid":192946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"那些年 每次前奏一響起就有那時著住校服追女仔既畫面"},{"pid":"c86933bb36d75c4f3488ebcde1e7cda2ac47d02c","tid":768423,"uid":70763,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"如果某時期聽得多某首歌<br />\n咁第日聽返就會有嗰個時期既畫面同感覺<br />\n啲歌對我嚟講似時光機既一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63fafe52963e3e0803fc22f8babd8f93c1ebde0","tid":768423,"uid":64450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:34:40.000Z","msg":"超有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5a11c7561a5ba72d554793b80b18cbe16ad6d1","tid":768423,"uid":32783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"係 聽到thinking out loud好有冬天感覺"},{"pid":"2656d0fd28b808ba387cf09ea599b853749bb7d6","tid":768423,"uid":36673,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:37:29.000Z","msg":"歌係一樣會幫你保存記憶既野，好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如個首歌同人分享過/係他人分享比你，一聽就會記起對方<br />\n最愛既歌唔好亂比人聽，唔係就會唔敢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51b494339ffc9329726c00ba912468b56491047","tid":768423,"uid":36103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:53:28.000Z","msg":"擁抱 一聽啲蟬聲就好有夏季感覺 同埋我第一次聽就係嗰個我失戀嘅夏天"},{"pid":"0c5b5ed95785a83431c71221e3f9cb39996aaf98","tid":768423,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2656d0fd28b808ba387cf09ea599b853749bb7d6","tid":768423,"uid":36673,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:37:29.000Z","msg":"歌係一樣會幫你保存記憶既野，好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如個首歌同人分享過/係他人分享比你，一聽就會記起對方<br />\n最愛既歌唔好亂比人聽，唔係就會唔敢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7aa60d147d0b02ce1fc0071ac0c2d282783a68","tid":768423,"uid":125611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:43:24.000Z","msg":"會啊<br />\n以前中學冬天較果個鬧鐘鈴聲係首日文歌<br />\n而家聽翻都覺得涷<br />\n諗起得十度朝早六點要起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1598dd62ef21c25acf6abba7bbd925e71826405e","tid":768423,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:44:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xdv83MFJd7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXdv83MFJd7U&d=rJonw%2FOR30HaaENIyD0zgqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7b783a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xdv83MFJd7U</a><br />\nWestlife - Seasons In The Sun (Official Video)<br />\n<br />\n同首歌名有分別，唔知點解一聽就覺得係冬天<br />\n可能同 MV 入面所有人著冬天長袖衫有關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a586daef13fc15d0183cc3a7a50fb1b3cd396dd","tid":768423,"uid":170624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:55:22.000Z","msg":"季節得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個陣中秋節 玩到好夜之後一個人搭的士番屋企<br />\n架車好慢所以好靜 得好清無雜音嘅收音機聲<br />\n<br />\n望到隔住塊車窗嘅月亮又大又圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n禁啱收音機播王菀之首月亮說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （第一次聽）<br />\n個feel好難形容 <br />\n但從此一聽月亮說就諗起中秋過後獨自回家有少少寂寞嘅心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41457e999e575a0ca86ee2c23838d50676a83e30","tid":768423,"uid":170624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:56:06.000Z","msg":"[quote]<span style=\"color: red;\">節日</span>得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}